definitions.text:
@ngoan ngoãn
* adj
- docile; obedient

@ngoan cường
- With stamina and sense of purpose, dogged
=Cuộc chiến đấu ngoan cường+A fight full of stamina and sense of purpose

@ngoang ngoảng
- (ít dùng) Quite empty, considerably empty
=Bán một lúc thúng xôi ngoang ngoảng quá nửa+Her sticky rice basket was more than half empty after only a moment's business

@ngoao
- Mew, miaou, miaow
=Con mèo kêu ngoao ngoao+The kitten was crying "Miaou, miaou"

@ngoan cố
* adj
- stubborn; obstinate; contumacious
